This egg contains one random mini from set 1, 2, or 3. Minis are tiny models of your favorite monsters and characters from the world of Tyria. Minis can also be used as components for Mystic Forge recipes.

Only found in the Grove's social clubs, it's said this will make you move like a reed in the wind.
Gain bonus power, which is increased when wielding a dagger.
Deal more damage to foes with a lower health percentage than you.

Brave Adventurer,
Strange things have been happening in the world beyond Tyria. Things we took for granted about how we understood the systems of the Mists have been shattered, and now Dessa needs help! Words of your heroism have even reached me here in Mistlock Observatory deep within the Mists. If you are up to the challenge, join a party of adventurers and travel to meet me from the portal in Lion's Arch.

Things that we've seen change:
 —Fractal runs only consist of one island now, instead of four!
 —New weapons have been spotted deeper in the fractals.
 —Ascended breathing apparatuses have been discovered!
 —New daily achievements have been added.

Also, I believe I've discovered the path to building a precursor backpack! Come find me in the Fractals of the Mists if you want to know more!

—Kelvei, Legendary Observer of Dessa's Krewe
Summon a Centaur Banner at your objective. This banner provides the wielder access to powerful offensive skills, as well as a break bar.
Used to craft the backpack Upper Bound. Extras can be purchased from the Aetherblade Quartermaster in the Captain Mai Trin Boss fractal for Balls of Dark Energy.
When you successfully evade an attack, gain vigor.
Double-click this potion to gain a hero point.
The Mordrem have begun invading Brisban Wildlands!
<c=@abilitytype>Signets</c> gain reduced recharge, improved passive effects, and share their passive effects with nearby allies when activated.
